results.description: Originally we wanted to do some astrophotography over this lake as the Milky Way aligned itself perfectly just above the 10 peaks in Moraine Lake. Unfortunately, the skies became clouded with the mustiness from the forest fires that have been happening in B.C for the past week. We also ran out of gas and that got us stranded for the night and ended up sleeping in the car and waited next morning for the gas stations to open up. Nonetheless, we decided to just drive up to the lake anyway and take advantage of us being in Banff.
